Description:
100% Locally Owned and Operated
We sell weed and showcase local art. 

       Here at FivePoint we're passionate about Canadian cannabis, and our mission is to support local economy. We purchase small production, Canadian made goods. Not only will you find a curated list of some of Canada's best bud, concentrates, edibles, beverages and vapes but you will find lots of custom glass, one-of-a-kind accessories not available anywhere else, and Canadian made products.

     We are committed to supporting local art in the FivePoint gallery space. Featured exhibitions of paintings, sculptures and furniture contribute to a laid-back and creative atmosphere focused on community and education. It is our goal to continue to make measurable impacts for local artists.

     When you purchase products at FivePoint, your money is directly going back to local artists in your community, and your dollars are being reinvested back into Canadian companies. Shop local, enjoy art, smoke good weed. That's what we care about, too.

Sativa Bliss Cannabis Boutique is a chain of licensed cannabis stores with locations throughout Ontario. We are an independent, Canadian owned & operated Cannabis Retail Company. We are passionate about the cannabis industry! We are committed to providing a unique shopping experience. Our stores proudly showcase real products so you can see everything we have to offer as you browse our stores. We are committed to provide a safe and welcoming environment for new and existing cannabis users, offering a unique shopping experience with a wide range of high-quality cannabis products and accessories at affordable price points. At Sativa Bliss our focus is on creating happy customers one person at a time. Our knowledgeable staff are marijuana enthusiasts and available for consultation- happy to help you find what you are looking for. Our budtenders educate our customers about all things cannabis. We can talk to you all day about weed, bongs, pipes, vapes, edibles and everything in between. 

 

We offer a large selection of cannabis products, whether you are a connoisseur or new to the world of cannabis, we can help you find or recommend the right products for your lifestyle.
